name: Seven WishStones for Guidance Safety
description:
This is a bootleg of GissyEva's webseries. You don't need to watch it for context, but I'm sure Gissy would appreciate the watch.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IH5ke5K3i3A&

This is submitted for the "So Bad It's Good Jam" with the modifier "impossible." Expect a lot of impossible things here.. (but there is a credits screen)

Thanks to the amazing voice talent!

Rosy Rose - RoniX

Jingle Clown - Violett

Yahoo Girl - Tyangerine

Princess Malarky - PoundToundHound

Muscle Guy - Me

Sword Lord - FunnyBunnyJay

Narrator - JellyFishtheActor61

Gisselle was supposed to voice in the game but hearing her voice in this game is impossible.. like many things in the game.
